overview: Paris By Night 129 - Dynasty is the 138th Paris By Night program (including special programs) produced and published by Thuy Nga center. This is the first program to gather the top singers of the two music dynasties, Lu Lien, Pham Duy, including: Tuan Ngoc, Khanh Ha, Thuy Anh, Luu Bich, Thai Hien, Thai Thao, .. The program was dubbed the "most anticipated Paris By Night program of 2019".
title: Paris By Night 129 - Dynasty
